(40, 26, 13, 19, 112, 6, 6, 'be told for a memorial of her', 'Remembrance of the Righteous', 'This connection highlights the theme of remembrance in both passages. Matthew emphasizes that the woman''s act will be told for a memorial, while Psalms speaks of the righteous being in everlasting remembrance.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
